            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4">The Bulgarian Prodigy: Karlos Nasar’s Road to Olympic Gold</h1>

            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4 text-muted">
                <span class="me-3">By MaxEndLabs Editorial</span>
                <span class="me-3">|</span>
                <span>February 2026</span>
            </div>

            <img src="https://bnrnews.bg/api/media/32fc2fcc-1b7f-437a-9011-a607404af980?Size=large" 
